   version stable 5.0.0 4.8.5 4.8.4
   require bison readline tk
  category network
 attribute makej x11
    source http://ftp.isc.org/isc/IRRToolSet/IRRToolSet-$VERSION/irrtoolset-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info home  http://www.isc.org/software/irrtoolset
 freshmeat irrtoolset
      desc 'policy analysis tools for routing

IRRToolSet is a set of policy analysis tools, written in C++.
It is designed to run under UNIX, using Tcl/Tk for graphics.
There are tools for generating router configuration files, 
displaying and checking routes, generating aggregations of 
networks, etc.
This project was formerly known as the Routing Arbiter ToolSet 
(RAToolset), and was maintained by ISI.'
